message: Hello Bob, I'm offering this product for $20,000. I believe it will be highly beneficial for you.
Hello Alice, thanks for your offer. That's quite high for me though. I'd be willing to pay $12,000 for it.
Thanks for the offer, Bob. I understand your position, but the product's value is quite a bit higher for me. How about we meet in the middle at $17,000?
I appreciate you working with me Alice.  $14,000 is the highest I can go.
